    <h1>OpenTelemetry Native ESM Demo</h1>
    <p>This demo shows native OpenTelemetry auto-instrumentation using Node.js ESM loader hooks.</p>

    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Uses <code>node --import=./register.mjs</code> to load OpenTelemetry before the app</li>
      <li>Auto-instruments HTTP, Express, and other supported libraries</li>
      <li>No middleware required - instrumentation happens at the Node.js level</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <pre><code>bun run build
bun run start:prod</code></pre>

    <h2>Limitations</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Only works in production builds (not dev mode)</li>
      <li>Not all instrumentations support ESM yet</li>
    </ul>

